sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User Client
    participant A as Attacker
    participant S1 as Service A
    participant S2 as Service B

    U->>S2: Call with token aud=service-b
    A->>S1: Replay token aud=service-b
    S1-->>A: Access granted (if audience check is weak)

    A->>S1: Send ID token instead of access token
    S1-->>A: Access granted (if token-type checks are missing)
